Collections.rule:
Individual:
	@A*
Types:
	'Pressure Observation'
Facts:
	'made by sensor' @C*,
	'observed property' VGR_1_Pneumatic_System_Pressure,
	'used procedure' @G*,
	'has_result' @A*(mm:append("_Result")),
	'result time'@F*(xsd:dateTime)
Annotations:
	rdfs:comment @A*(mm:append(" is an individual from type Pressure Observation"))

Individual:
	@A*(mm:append("_Result"))
Types:
	'Pressure Result'
Facts:
	'has_pressure' @E*(xsd:float)
Annotations:
	rdfs:comment @A*(mm:append("_Result is a pressure result measured at  ", @F*))
